race.description: Follow Thedogssa On X Open Stake Pr2 Division1
race.comment: SKETCHY SHOW MAN (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Gawler in a handy 22.85 beating Indie Or Jill. Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. ONE MARGARITA (2) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and two minors from seven tries. Below best last time at Gawler (23.64) in a Other, finishing a 9 length fifth. Can feature in the finish. SOUTH BOYS (1) drew this same box last time when a 1.75 lengths winner (16.76) in a Grade 5 over 300m at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. BUDGEREE (7) is worth a look over a shorter trip this time.
